high_descs: Turn right to face the counter between the toilet and the sink
Pick up the candle in front of the bar of soap
Turn to the right and go to the sink near the bathtub
Open the far right cabinet door under the sink and put the candle in on the right side
Turn right toward the bathtub
Pick up the candle by the faucet
Turn right to face the sink on the right
Open the cabinet under the sink and place the candle to the left of the other candle
anns.task_desc: Put two candles in the cabinet under the sink

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the door, then hang a right and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the closest candle off of the counter.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, then hang a left and walk up to towards the tub, stop at the end of the counter and turn to face it.
Open the rightmost lower cabinet door and put the candle inside on the front right edge, then close the cabinet.
Walk over to the tub on your right.
Pick up the candle off of the tub.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn right and walk forward, turn right again to face the counter.
Open the rightmost lower cabinet door and put the candle inside to the left of the candle that's already in there, then close the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Move two candles into a cabinet.

high_descs: turn around and walk over to the left side of the bathroom sink
grab a candle off of the back side of the bathroom counter there
move over to the right side of the bathroom sink cabinet
place the candle inside the bottom right bathroom sink cabinet
turn right to face the bath tub, and approach the bath tub
grab the candle off of the back left side of the bath tub
move to face the right side of the bathroom cabinet again
place the candle in the same cabinet you put the other candle in, which is the bottom right cabinet of the bathroom cabinet
anns.task_desc: place two candles inside the bathroom cabinet
